###
#
# Update Work Metrics
#
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/burnout/WorkMetrics(26)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avg_working_hours": 9.0,
  "overtime_hours": 3.5
}

###
#
# Create Burnout Metrics Entry
#
